00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:37,740
 but worshiping Caesar, right?

293
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:40,880
 And so there was sort of this ritual

294
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:45,200
 that you would have to pay tribute to Caesar once a year.

