00:22:31,260 --> 00:22:34,180
 accepted by Christ as children of God.

373
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:36,940
 And we are free in Christ

374
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:40,760
 to go and proclaim his message wherever he calls us to.

