00:22:47,060 --> 00:22:48,080
 imprison them.

377
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:53,500
 And I hope that we, no matter who is going against us,

378
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:58,500
 that we would boldly proclaim the message of Christ,

379
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:00,740
 the gospel of Christ,

380
00:23:00,740 --> 00:23:05,620
 rich, accepted and free.

